-- Kuwait to Act Against Writer on Saudi, U.A.E. Article, KUNA Says
-- B y   D a h l i a   K h o l a i f
-- 2012-10-31T05:20:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-31/kuwait-to-act-against-writer-on-saudi-u-a-e-article-kuna-says.html
Kuwait ’s Foreign Ministry said an
article written by Mohammed Abdelkader al-Jassim on Saudi Arabia
and the U.A.E. was offensive and harms brotherly ties between
Kuwait and the two states, KUNA, the state-run news agency,
reported yesterday.  Al-Jassim’s article was published yesterday on an
electronic newspaper’s website, and the foreign ministry said it
would be taking action, KUNA said.  The writer has been detained in the past and was most
recently released in 2011.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Dahlia Kholaif in Kuwait at 
 dkholaif@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Shaji Mathew at 
 shajimathew@bloomberg.net  